{"id":14366,"date":"2024-02-10T18:26:04","date_gmt":"2020-09-10T12:56:04","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=14366"},"modified":"2022-02-08T21:54:58","modified_gmt":"2022-02-08T16:24:58","slug":"modern-farmhouse-design-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/modern-farmhouse-design-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"Modern Farmhouse Design Ideas For You!"},"content":{"rendered":"\r\n<p><em>A quick lowdown on modern farmhouse design ideas to help you get started!<\/em><\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>A harmonious combination of rustic and refined, modern farmhouse inspired <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">interior designs<\/a> continues to be a popular choice amongst urban families. Modern farmhouse interior designs are typically characterised by a neutral colour palette, wooden accents, and rustic furniture pieces with sharp lines.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>If you love the idea of designing a farmhouse style home we will help you take it to a whole new level! From farmhouse inspired bathrooms, kitchens to bedrooms and living rooms, we have created a lowdown of modern farmhouse design ideas to help you get inspired and started!<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>So let&#8217;s take a look at our personal favourite modern farmhouse designs\u2014inside and out.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Farmhouse Design &#8211; Front Porch<\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>First thing first, the exteriors! A modern farmhouse front porch design is usually an excellent mix of both modern and traditional details just like this stunning one here! Doesn&#8217;t this front porch remind you of those luxurious farmhouses that are perhaps designed to get featured in magazines? This modern minimalist front porch design is an excellent choice if you believe that less is more! This design features a pergola, a comfortable couch, and an armchair with a footrest. An accent wall complements the overall colour scheme of this modern farmhouse exteriors.\u00a0<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" class=\"wp-image-14370\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181515\/modern-farmhouse-entry-exterior-front-porch.jpg\" alt=\"Modern farmhouse entry exterior designed with pergola, couch, and an armchair with a footrest is stunning.\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181515\/modern-farmhouse-entry-exterior-front-porch.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181515\/modern-farmhouse-entry-exterior-front-porch-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181515\/modern-farmhouse-entry-exterior-front-porch-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181515\/modern-farmhouse-entry-exterior-front-porch-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Living Room With A Modern Farmhouse Vibe<\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>In this spacious modern farmhouse style living room, the showstopper is the large windows with wooden frames. This living room further features wooden beams on the ceiling and an indoor fireplace designed with reclaimed materials. Furniture pieces like tufted velvet sofas and a vintage coffee table bring in old world charm. A soft colour palette, complementing decor like beaded frames on the wall, a classic blue rug with wooden accents wherever you look give this living room with a modern farmhouse vibe.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" class=\"wp-image-14373\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181833\/modern-farmhouse-living-room-design.jpg\" alt=\"Modern farmhouse style living room with large wooden windows, wooden ceiling, sofas and coffee table brings old-world charm.\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181833\/modern-farmhouse-living-room-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181833\/modern-farmhouse-living-room-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181833\/modern-farmhouse-living-room-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181833\/modern-farmhouse-living-room-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\r\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Do you want a free design consultation, call our designers\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28125622\/do-you-want-free-design-consultation.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Farmhouse Kitchen Design<\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>A modern farmhouse kitchen design is practical, clutter-free, and always stylish. Inspired by the kitchens of classic American farmhouses, this beautiful kitchen design features soothing white cabinetry with reclaimed wooden accents. This stellar <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/modular-kitchen-design\/\">kitchen design<\/a> includes light and dark details for added visual appeal. The island or breakfast counter with bar stools cum chairs create a peaceful gathering place. Hardwood flooring blends well with the wooden beams on the ceiling. A pair of antique pendant lights with focus lights highlight the design details and bind this kitchen to perfection.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" class=\"wp-image-14372\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181722\/modern-farmhouse-kitchen-design.jpg\" alt=\"Modern farmhouse kitchen design and decor ideas with dining table are practical, clutter-free, and always stylish.\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181722\/modern-farmhouse-kitchen-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181722\/modern-farmhouse-kitchen-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181722\/modern-farmhouse-kitchen-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181722\/modern-farmhouse-kitchen-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Farmhouse Inspired Bedroom<\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>By now you are aware that modern farmhouse style is all about using natural materials to provide a rustic look while embracing modern sensibilities. It also includes a generous use of antiques and found objects as decor. Here, in this bedroom design a dried tree branch above the simple wooden headboard adds dollops of charm to this space. The black wall lends a modern touch. Decor here comprises wooden logs, a bohemian rug, indoor plants, potpourri and the delicate white sheers to keep the farmhouse vibe intact.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" class=\"wp-image-14368\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181306\/modern-farm-house-bedroom-design.jpg\" alt=\"Modern Farmhouse Bedroom design with dried tree branch, wooden headboard, rug &amp; potpourri is modern farmhouse interior design style.\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181306\/modern-farm-house-bedroom-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181306\/modern-farm-house-bedroom-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181306\/modern-farm-house-bedroom-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181306\/modern-farm-house-bedroom-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\r\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a free design consultation from design cafe\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/27144955\/get-free-design-consultation.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Reading Nook Is A Must<\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>If you are an avid reader or like to sit with a cup of coffee and read a book when you visit a farmhouse you will agree that a tiny little nook is a must for your home. Here, this stunning reading nook is a perfect example of\u00a0 modern farmhouse style of interiors. The earth-toned textured wall, wicker chair, a modern coffee table with a wooden disc as a tabletop, earthen pots painted in black and lush indoor plants makes this corner look like a reader&#8217;s dream lazy holiday! The showstopper? A bamboo pendant light.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" class=\"wp-image-14374\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181939\/modern-farmhouse-reading-nook.jpg\" alt=\"Beautiful modern farmhouses earth-toned textured wall, wicker chair, coffee table &amp; plants are the stunning reading nook.\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181939\/modern-farmhouse-reading-nook.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181939\/modern-farmhouse-reading-nook-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181939\/modern-farmhouse-reading-nook-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181939\/modern-farmhouse-reading-nook-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Farmhouse Inspired Outdoor Or Patio Seating<\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>This is a design element that you can consider adding in your balcony, patio, front porch or even the foyer area to bring home a lovely farmhouse vibe. Besides, this can be your next DIY furniture project as well! All you need is reclaimed wooden logs with a wooden plank to create a stunning modern farmhouse inspired outdoor or patio seating like the one shown in this image! Although these wooden benches are available in the market but if you are considering the whole DIY idea do use a coat of varnish to get rid of splinters.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" class=\"wp-image-14367\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181204\/farmhouse-modern-decor-outdoor-patio-seating-.jpg\" alt=\"Patio seating made from reclaimed wooden logs outdoor is a modern farmhouse architecture DIY.\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181204\/farmhouse-modern-decor-outdoor-patio-seating-.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181204\/farmhouse-modern-decor-outdoor-patio-seating--300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181204\/farmhouse-modern-decor-outdoor-patio-seating--768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181204\/farmhouse-modern-decor-outdoor-patio-seating--150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Explore, more about <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/seating-ideas-for-home\/\">Seating Ideas For Home<\/a><\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Farmhouse Style Of Decor<\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>The right approach to modern farmhouse style of decor is all about a low-key blend of rustic and found objects with a comfortable, peaceful vibe. Candles, wooden discs, lanterns, dried tree branches, crate boxes, delicate white drapes, fur and bohemian rugs, with soft coloured upholstery and a lot of pendant and spotlights will do wonders!<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" class=\"wp-image-14371\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181620\/modern-farmhouse-interior-design-style.jpg\" alt=\"Farmhouse modern decor with candles, wooden discs, lanterns, dried tree branches &amp; pendant light brings rustic feel.\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181620\/modern-farmhouse-interior-design-style.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181620\/modern-farmhouse-interior-design-style-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181620\/modern-farmhouse-interior-design-style-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/10181620\/modern-farmhouse-interior-design-style-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>And it&#8217;s a wrap! We hope these suggestions help you design a modern home with a farmhouse vibe or design a farmhouse of your own!\u00a0<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\"